      <abstract id="aspace_b4c1c2b02e205f6dc4445cfaa4fe40da">Helen S. Bevington was a poet and
        taught in the Dept. of English at Duke University from 1943-1976. The collection includes
        page and galley proofs and typescripts. It ranges in date from 1965-1976.</abstract>
